object.name: getMyDefaultAdministratorRights
object.description: Use this method to get the current default administrator rights of the bot. Returns ChatAdministratorRights on success.
object.html_description: Use this method to get the current default administrator rights of the bot. Returns ChatAdministratorRights on success.
object.rst_description: Use this method to get the current default administrator rights of the bot. Returns :class:`aiogram.types.chat_administrator_rights.ChatAdministratorRights` on success.

annotations.description: Pass True to get default administrator rights of the bot in channels. Otherwise, default administrator rights of the bot for groups and supergroups will be returned.
annotations.html_description: Pass True to get default administrator rights of the bot in channels. Otherwise, default administrator rights of the bot for groups and supergroups will be returned.
annotations.rst_description: Pass :code:`True` to get default administrator rights of the bot in channels. Otherwise, default administrator rights of the bot for groups and supergroups will be returned.
annotations.name: for_channels
